game.name: My Pet Clinic
game.description:
Have you ever imagined of performing an animal doctor in your life? Do you love pets and animals and like to handle issues related to them? If this is the case, this brand new animal game is definitely for you. You have a popular pet clinic of the city where you deal with kinds of medical problems related to multiple types of animals on your hand. Today some pets with different health issues have come to your clinic. Are you free enough to handle them? Join My Pet Clinic and be prepared to provide them with the needful medical attention! 

As an honest pet doctor, you will treat each pet with the needful medicines and treatment. These pets include parrots, rabbits, turtles, dogs and cats. You have to perform multiple medical activities to treat their problems and help them get back to their normal life. These things include adding crutches to the wounded parrots, cleaning and buffing turtle shells, giving eye drop solutions to cats, and removing stubborn ticks from dog fur. Use the hints to cure their problems in no time in this girls game! 

Remember that every animal comes with a different issue so be careful while taking care of them. Put your complete doctoring abilities to the test to help bring them back to the full health once again by just following the on-screen instructions! It will be an amazing experience to treat five different types of pets in an appropriate manner. Good luck to help all the cute pets to enjoy a health life again! Do not let them feel down and do every possible effort to make them happy in this fun veterinarian game.
